        <!--description list: NOT assignment objectives-->

        <h4>Description list: NOT part of objectives</h4>
        <hr>
        <dl style="background-color:rgb(99, 90, 99); border: 2 px solid">
            <dt>required</dt>
            <dd>Indicates that a field must be filled out before the form can be submitted.</dd>
            <hr>
            <br>
            <dt>pattern</dt>
            <dd>Specifies a regular expression that the input value must match.</dd>
            <br>
            <hr>
            <br>
            <dt>min</dt>
            <dd>Used with numeric fields like and date pickers to define a range of valid values. </dd>
            <hr>
            <br>
            <dt>max</dt>
            <dd>Used with numeric fields like and date pickers to define a range of valid values.</dd>
            <hr>
            <br>
            <dt>step</dt>
            <dd>Also used with numeric fields to specify the allowed increment or decrement steps.</dd>
            <hr>
            <br>
        </dl>

